{"tid":1905071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】皇恩浩蕩，中國捐2.5萬口罩給韓國","createTime":"2020-03-01T04:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T05:21:33.000Z","uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f3fde24934fd2bbc98111ec6d1edbef3a958c89a","tid":1905071,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）肆虐，中國與韓國成為疫情重災區，昨（27）日中國駐韓國大使館為大邱市緊急籌備的2.5萬個醫用口罩，從首爾明洞中國大使館整裝起運；中國駐韓國大使邢海明表示：「韓國的困難，就是我們的困難！」<br />\n<br />\n據《人民日報》報導，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國駐韓國大使館捐了<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.5萬個</span></ins>醫用口罩給大邱，運送愛心口罩的貨車上，懸掛著新羅旅唐學者崔致遠的名句「道不遠人、人無異國」，以及「大邱加油！韓國加油！」的醒目標語。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%91%E6%88%9A%E8%88%87%E5%85%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8D%902-5%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%B5%A6%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B-052545985.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%2588%259A%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%25B1-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258D%25902-5%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B-052545985.html&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGouoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=86bfa396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%91%E6%88%9A%E8%88%87%E5%85%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8D%902-5%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%B5%A6%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B-052545985.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【回帶】<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1月30日報導指出，文在寅政府決議對中國捐助<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">200萬副口罩、10萬件防護衣和10萬副護目鏡</span></ins></span></span>，文在寅說，病毒不是我們唯一面對的東西，我們應該積極對抗過度的焦慮與模糊的恐懼，而保護人民免於武漢肺炎疫情的不是恐怖和憎恨，而是信任和合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3060146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3060146&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGouoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=40a160fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3060146&h=34877d8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3060146</a>"},{"pid":"4880cfac3f74f2ee816c04a56c08490b24b14caa","tid":1905071,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T04:21:38.000Z","msg":"哇 咁撚多呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ca1f8b25c3853b6b1768b2312aeb0a95210f06","tid":1905071,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T04:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95f4d3b0e54bb76f447dd44c1a7749ebc513717","tid":1905071,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"兩萬五個，如果一包包咁裝，只係兩三箱嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}